{"tid":1415481,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好啦 勇武完 爽完啦 係時候做正經野","createTime":"2019-08-05T13:47:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T16:06:53.000Z","uid":54250,"like":240,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"d5d6d7f09beb30292c56b27aa83d4b8a24885f38","tid":1415481,"uid":54250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:47:05.000Z","msg":"我知今日士氣好高湃<br />\n但冷靜落黎 要做賽後檢討<br />\n今日勇武係正<br />\n但放火好明顯真係未係時候<br />\n唔係話割𥱊 但身邊個民意同風向係轉轉地<br />\n<br />\n係時候到和理飛出場 比人地了解我地點解咁做<br />\n主要係同天水圍女仔出氣<br />\n比要人知我地同暴徒分別<br />\n<br />\n唔好比人帶到風向 比怒火支配<br />\n我都好憤怒 但唔好還發洩而做<br />\n要將怒火轉開去<br />\n<br />\n目標係暴力政權 五大訴求 決一不可<br />\n清算黑警 光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n手足要保持頭腦清醒啊！"},{"pid":"e3eead7cb3fc1472e93789554373c404af91974e","tid":1415481,"uid":54250,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:47:41.000Z","msg":"推上去比手足清醒下"},{"pid":"11ab8577ddde6787a46eecb64099ee6ad8f9cfd2","tid":1415481,"uid":12179,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:48:19.000Z","msg":"大家唔好被仇恨支配自己，在危難中，仍要時刻保持警覺與思考<br />\nBy天琦"},{"pid":"524cb74d439bd14fcd63ea69b78c03c76af48352","tid":1415481,"uid":54250,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:48:22.000Z","msg":"冷靜啲 我知就開學 時間唔多<br />\n但唔可以行錯每一步"},{"pid":"93968a144c6074240b1e5e90c886273e0d0308a7","tid":1415481,"uid":106870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:48:49.000Z","msg":"不要説：失民意，試著説：一齊贏翻民意<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1415350\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1415350</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a2070d77c258e20eb9b51af82d4ac71e6f314347","tid":1415481,"uid":113148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:49:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"12d50076b4016159a4440f9ff67c9dbd9ef01ea8","tid":1415481,"uid":