,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:55:01.000Z","msg":"我地仲有機場 五大訴求啊 <br />\n入黎同我光復香港啦"},{"pid":"9443e104ee1c1344734ef5a9c8ddd5d13c67a916","tid":1415481,"uid":279874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:55:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eba89982c5a9c58954aa7f7959ca821b20456020","tid":1415481,"uid":140738,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:55:11.000Z","msg":"同意係時候停一停到和理非<br />\n<br />\n我覺得依家應該靜一個星期<br />\n<br />\n比個限期set條底線佢處理問題<br />\n<br />\n過左依個底線之後而無做任何野<br />\n<br />\n我地再出多一次黎玩<br />\n<br />\n咁做係話比政府聽已經比左好多時間你地<br />\n<br />\n你都係咩都做唔到<br />\n<br />\n我地就更加出師有名<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n文宣可以話比大眾聽<br />\n<br />\n我地示威者能放能收<br />\n<br />\n依家比足時間政府但都係做唔到野<br />\n<br />\n提醒返大眾所有野都係政府嘅錯"},{"pid":"32c5c66c59c800c675197de796f8940ac990c8f5","tid":1415481,"uid":54250,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:55:25.000Z","msg":"我唔想成也連登 敗也連登"},{"pid":"eadb73b9e87e8bae41c0074d325473f12b665d38","tid":1415481,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:56:12.000Z","msg":"強調不分化，唔等於要失去獨立思考能力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1415149\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1415149</a><br />\n<br />\n請不要摧毀初心<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1415059\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1415059</a><br />\n<br />\n問題唔在於玩火 問題在於無差別攻擊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1414453\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1414453</a><br />\n<br />\n你地重未明政府玩緊乜？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1414221\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1414221</a><br />\n<br />\n天琦真係講得好中 ，唔少人已經比仇恨沖昏左頭腦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1414402\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1414402</a>"},{"pid":"348aaf1437a2da54c04c4f5fe5c09e39b3c0c957","tid":1415481,"uid":54250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:57:04.000Z","msg":"係時候set 低線啦 <br />\n同意啊 做左樣比政府睇我地可以玩幾大<br />\n再唔會應就再玩準啲 <br />\n下次法師會再升lv<img 